"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/758069","HM Treasury","false","2017-09-15","<p>I will be writing to chairs of the pay review bodies in due course following the usual process.</p>","South West Norfolk","Elizabeth Truss",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/758069/answer",,,,,,,,,"2017-09-15T10:55:07.733Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/758069/answer","Biography information for Elizabeth Truss","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/758069/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2017-09-06","Public Sector: Pay","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, if he will make it his policy to issue remit letters to the chairs of the pay review bodies for the 2018-19 pay round before the 2017 Autumn Budget.","false","Biography information for Alex Norris","Nottingham North","Alex Norris","9141"
